Bundled open-source icon embedding index (icons.bundled.v1.*)

Icon artwork sources (see manifest license.upstream for SPDX):

- Material Design Icons — Apache-2.0 — https://github.com/Templarian/MaterialDesign-SVG
- Tabler Icons — MIT — https://github.com/tabler/tabler-icons
- Fluent UI System Icons — MIT — https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui-system-icons
- Font Awesome Free — see https://fontawesome.com/license/free

embeddings.bin is derived from rasterized PNG templates embedded with MobileCLIP2-S0.
Index format: MCL2 v1 (fp32) or v2 (int8 per-vector scale).
The same index pack is used on desktop (ONNX embed) and mobile (MNN embed); only the runtime embed model differs.
